Using @@ykeep@@N will recall you to your keep.
Using @@ykeep create@@N creates your keep with @@yno_teleport@@N, @@yno_bloodwalk@@N,
@@yno_portal@@N, @@yno_mob@@N, and @@ysafe@@N flags.
Using @@ykeep title <string>@@N while inside your keep will update your keep's
title.
Using @@ykeep desc <string>@@N while inside your keep will update your keep's
description.
Using @@ykeep regen@@N while inside your keep adds the @@yregen@@N room flag for
@@Y100@@N quest points.
Using @@ykeep inside@@N while inside your keep adds the @@yinside@@N room flag for
@@Y50@@N quest points.
Using @@ykeep storage@@N while inside your keep expands keep chest capacity by
@@Y5@@N slots. Cost is tiered at @@Y50@@N quest points per tier: @@Y50->55 = 50@@N,
@@Y55->60 = 100@@N, @@Y60->65 = 150@@N, and so on.
Using @@ykeep healer@@N while inside your keep purchases a personal healer for
@@Y250@@N quest points. This purchase is permanent and can only be done once.